                            // Nova-body –≤ core.nv —З–µ—А–µ–Ј DeclaredBody +
                            // closure invoke —З–µ—А–µ–Ј NovaClosBase cast.
                            // Plan 99.3 –§.1: Option.map(f) вЖТ Nova-body
